parameters.name: KeyPairName
parameters.description:
The name of the key pair. The name must be 2 to 128 characters in length. The name must start with a letter but cannot start with `http://` or `https://`. The name can contain the following characters:

*   Digits
*   :
*   \_
*   *

You can specify only one name. By default, all key pairs are queried.

parameters.name: PageNumber
parameters.description: The page number of the returned page. Valid values: integers that are greater than 0. Default value: 1.

parameters.name: PageSize
parameters.description: The number of entries per page. Valid values: integers that are greater than 0. Default value: 10.
